https://scienceofmind.org/how-to-increase-brain-capacity-to-100/  

Explores neuroplasticity, the brain’s ability to rewire itself.

Offers strategies like:
Mindfulness and meditation
Brain-stimulating activities
Nutrition and supplements

Emphasizes that mental performance can be trained and expanded

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
While we use all of our brain structurally, we might not be using our full cognitive potential:
Many people don’t train memory, focus, or creativity regularly.
Neuroplasticity shows the brain can rewire and improve with effort.
Emotional intelligence, intuition, and imagination are often neglected in traditional education.

So while the 10% figure is a myth, the idea of unlocking greater mental capacity through training, mindfulness, and learning is very real.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

